187.0	Haruki_Murakami	Haruki Murakami	Haruki Murakami Murakami Haruki, born January 12, 1949) is a Japanese writer and translator. His works of fiction and non-fiction have garnered him critical acclaim and numerous awards, including the Franz Kafka Prize and Jerusalem Prize among others.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/75/HarukiMurakami.png/220px-HarukiMurakami.png
